raw_body: WIJETUNGE – M.H.D. TISSA – (Formerly of the Department of Town & Country Planning and in Uganda,​ Nigeria,​ Qatar and Australia),​ passed away on 14th in Sydney,​ Australia after a long illness. He was the husband and step father of Jembu & Sukie and the brother of Peter,​ Matilda and the late Alfred and Gamini. 00610432919374.041583
